impactDescription:
We wish to share the impact our contributions had on Optimism Collective:

⭐ ️ Increase in the number of Optimism developers and medical eco-system users onboarded to Optimism from 20 to 50 in India. Pilot Deployments at Rajshri Medical College & Hospital; Covid Care Center & S.M.S. School, Delhi;
⭐️Increase in the number of OP developers, users investing in Optimism and our key OP stack modules, health projects built on Optimism  from 10 to 25;
⭐️Improved collaboration with other OP projects to increase the number of partner projects utilizing OP Medicine’s modules by 2 to 15;
⭐️OP solutions for soul bonding ID, interoperability, sharding tools & NFT marketplaces of DICOM data enable development of Web3 projects like Medi Assist for medical counseling and insurance, billing platform.

